Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: The twine used in hay balers to tie up hay bales. This was also used by farmers as an even more flexible No. 8 wire for repairs and emergencies and for keeping up trousers as a substitute for belt or braces.
